Package: rdkafka
Type: Package
Title: R wrapper for librdkafka
Version: 0.1.0
Maintainer: Li Gen <libingfei@sina.com>
Description: Provides an implementation of the Producer and Consumer clients using the Apache Kafka protocol through the C library librdkafka. 
             See <https://kafka.apache.org/> and <https://github.com/confluentinc/librdkafka> and <https://github.com/confluentinc/librdkafka> for more information.
